---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 144
By: William Law
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Renunciation-Detachment=Eluding the Ego
  - Sacrifice-Death=Sacrifice and Suffering=Austerity not to Be Sought
---
All the activity of man in the works of self-denial has no good in itself,
but is only to open an entrance for the one only Good, the light of God, to
operate upon us.
